GULF OF MEXICO.
WESTERN CARIBBEAN SEA.
DNC 15.
1. MARINERS ARE ADVISED TO DISPOSE OF RECENTLY
   RECEIVED DNCDX015 ED.NO.036 DISC DUE TO
   THE DISTRIBUTION OF INCORRECT DATA.
2. DLA WILL DISTRIBUTE A CORRECT
   DNCDX015 ED.NO.036 DISC IMMEDIATELY.
3. CORRECT DATA IS AVAILABLE ON NGA WEBSITES AT
   https://www.geointel.nga.mil/products/dnc/#updated
   OR FROM THE SIPR SITE.
